NAME
    Dist::Zilla::App::Command::podpreview - preview munged pod in browser

VERSION
    version 0.002

SYNOPSIS
        dzil podpreview My::Module

DESCRIPTION
    A Dist::Zilla command to preview the munged pod of a module in a browser
    using App::PodPreview.

SEE ALSO
    *   Dist::Zilla

    *   App::PodPreview

